<body>
  <ul><!-- This is a list of the ingredients needed to prepare the dish-->
    <li>Onion</li>
    <li>Egg</li>
    <li>Tomato</li>
    <li>Flour</li>
    <li>Palm Oil</li>
    <li>Water.</li>
    <li>Seasoning.</li>
  </ul>
  <ol><!-- This is how to prepare the dish -->
    <li>Pour Water in a bowl, then measure two cups of flour, and mix it with sufficient amount of water.</li>
    <li>Add the eggs and mix thoroughly.</li>
    <li>Slice the tomato and Onions very nicely and Put them all together.</li>
    <li>Add seasoning</li>
    <li>Fry with a Palm oil and Have a nice Meal.</li>
  </ol>
